{"tid":51404,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"任何感情，一個人放棄，兩個人皆輸","createTime":"2016-12-23T07:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T03:22:05.000Z","uid":32734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a7673584ab4b2c27d38c44edffa6dbc675e766d","tid":51404,"uid":32734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:50:07.000Z","msg":"決定得一齊<br />\n有咩事咪兩個人面對<br />\n只係逃避問題依然存在<br />\n一來就用分開做方法直情不負責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da3a979457d4d25216a599ce76c25e2b3499677","tid":51404,"uid":7615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061204d11d0355b33f1b262eeeae44027c3d94b8","tid":51404,"uid":29203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"定係一直逃避問題嘅係你"},{"pid":"a8a4cd875d037a2f1a9bae474147f8e6f622794d","tid":51404,"uid":69130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:55:42.000Z","msg":"可能唔想比負擔你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf060564c051ecf13fbe41ade3f0975286dfc2c","tid":51404,"uid":32734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:53:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>定係一直逃避問題嘅係你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我發現問題，不過忍咗一排<br />\n到尋日拎咗出來講<br />\n但佢逃避問題<br />\n話要分開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d081e19c50e2938d22765fc6740f109bbf9be2","tid":51404,"uid":32734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能唔想比負擔你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實兩個人一齊負擔先解決到問題<br />\n自己覺得對對方好<br />\n但係咪真係好？<br />\n兩個人一齊<br />\n應該事事都關大家事<br />\n我反而想佢比我承受<br />\n都好過佢自己逃避<br />\n<br />\nSorry我發咗絲打你發脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f8324ad1521d32229483ce528ad64936167328","tid":51404,"uid":58810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:44:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>決定得一齊<br />\n有咩事咪兩個人面對<br />\n只係逃避問題依然存在<br />\n一來就用分開做方法直情不負責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當佢生命有比你更吸引既人/事<br />\n仲洗乜同你面對問題攞苦黎辛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227638fbf3c44cb4649a091e4de568226ad7f7f8","tid":51404,"uid":32734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:22:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>決定得一齊<br />\n有咩事咪兩個人面對<br />\n只係逃避問題依然存在<br />\n一來就用分開做方法直情不負責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當佢生命有比你更吸引既人/事<br />\n仲洗乜同你面對問題攞苦黎辛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講得啱啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}